text: Les Ablettes was a 20th-century French punk-rock band from Fumel (Lot-et- Garonne, New Aquitaine). They charted in 1987 in France when the single "Jackie s'en fout" reached No. 46. ==References== Category:French punk rock groups Category:Year of establishment missing Category:French musical groups from Nouvelle-Aquitaine
title: Les Ablettes
